 <li style="font-family: 'Century Gothic', 'MS Sans Serif', arial; font-size: 15px; text-align:left; line-height:150%; margin:0px; color:#000000; clear:both;">4 BILLION pounds of trash are dumped into the ocean in each year. We need to save the ocean before its too late</li>
